BREAK_POINT
We are a team of DIY enthusiasts from St. Petersburg and the Far East, passionate about experiments and powerful, driving sound.
Without being tied to genres or trying to evoke a feeling of nostalgia, we use retro consoles to get a new, unusual sound in hard-door electronic motives.
To get the sounds you want, we go beyond the usual music-making tools.
and we use programming, electronics and creativity.
